## Proposed changes

```
curl --location-trusted -u root:"" -T data.json  -H"format:json" http://127.0.0.1:8030/api/db/user1/_stream_load -H "jsonpaths: [\"$.NAME\", \"$.AGE\", \"$.AGENT_ID\"]"
```

before:
```
Reason: All fields is null, this is a invalid row.. src line [{"name":"Name 1","age":21,"agent_id":"1"}
]; 
```

after:
```
Reason: There is no column matching jsonpaths in the json file, columns:[name, age, agent_id, ], jsonpaths:["$.NAME", "$.AGE", "$.AGENT_ID"], please check columns and jsonpaths. src line [{"name":"Name 1","age":21,"agent_id":"1"}
]; 
```

